{"tid":2229030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「中共不等於中國」嚴格區別黨員人民","createTime":"2020-10-04T05:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T07:01:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4671350384400b552078fb08d2be1fd03ab3bb4a","tid":2229030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/CUHLGUVTKVB3LPRAEMRFWUMSME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FCUHLGUVTKVB3LPRAEMRFWUMSME%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=8f9534f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FCUHLGUVTKVB3LPRAEMRFWUMSME%2F&h=bd806aa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/CUHLGUVTKVB3LPRAEMRFWUMSME/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「中共不等於中國」嚴格區別黨員人民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pkx-1XMgzWe9y4IMWpqKtXLuKfs=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DCNZFQ5WMNDZZH5JLE33D57QRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPkx-1XMgzWe9y4IMWpqKtXLuKfs%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDCNZFQ5WMNDZZH5JLE33D57QRM.jpg&h=de8d1de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■海外華人上街呼籲國人退出中國共產黨、共青團和少先隊。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n前香港眾志主席羅冠聰表示，認為美國做法是「劍指中共」，措施明顯沿用「中共不等於中國」框架，預計針對中共的措施會逐步收緊。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美重啟冷戰政策 禁共產黨員申綠卡  羅冠聰：劍指中共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官二代共青團或受波及<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰在facebook撰文提到，相關指引涵蓋範圍相當廣泛，認為不單是指中共黨員，同時包括中共從屬或關聯團體成員，一眾官二代、共青團成員都有可能被波及。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，此次措施明顯沿用「中共不等於中國」框架，嚴格區別「中共」及「中國人民」，預計針對中共的措施會逐步收緊。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國移民與國籍法規定，共產黨及其附屬關聯組織的成員被禁止獲得綠卡的資格。與中國共產黨有關聯的其他組織亦有可能不被批准，關聯的意思包括「給予上述組織金錢或任何其他有價物」。<br />\n<br />\n申請者若虛報，或涉嫌移民欺詐罪。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook"},{"pid":"044595e33f5090705cc223f0cc35a62ccf50a52d","tid":2229030,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"香港全體公墓園算唔算？呢家做公墓園話要效忠中共訂立嘅國安法先做得"},{"pid":"a65e98e49c2bb5f147768bcfaf9e9bce51a97947","tid":2229030,"uid":274094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"我分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRSop1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRSop1d.png&h=c11006dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6K4mV7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6K4mV7U.jpg&h=331de520&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbapTUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbapTUA.jpg&h=ddac4611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVqEHNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVqEHNV.jpg&h=063af287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcHGV7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcHGV7W.jpg&h=52947866&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eiGbGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eiGbGh.jpg&h=56dc232f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqf5Dmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgqf5Dmi.jpg&h=b047603f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c75575d62df2fdbb5ac4c44c74ef14088f727e4","tid":2229030,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a5b126513334adb9f330fc62522fb13b2cea9b","tid":2229030,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n美國都係做緊呢一樣野<br />\n等於支共知道唔會有人黃轉藍<br />\n咁咪派人入黃圈分化<br />\n<br />\n支共=/=中國<br />\n批評支共 支共唔會出嚟講嘢<br />\n批評中國 支共就可以反擊<br />\n再自動情緒綁架14億人"},{"pid":"47a48de5b73d3c1727c9744fee684b0d8dafa193","tid":2229030,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"其實咪一撚樣<br />\n無支畜都唔會有支共"},{"pid":"ec75305683f50f120d65390ef4f77202a86c917f","tid":2229030,"uid":274094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a65e98e49c2bb5f147768bcfaf9e9bce51a97947","tid":2229030,"uid":274094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"我分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRSop1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRSop1d.png&h=c11006dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6K4mV7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6K4mV7U.jpg&h=331de520&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbapTUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbapTUA.jpg&h=ddac4611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVqEHNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVqEHNV.jpg&h=063af287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcHGV7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcHGV7W.jpg&h=52947866&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eiGbGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eiGbGh.jpg&h=56dc232f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqf5Dmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgqf5Dmi.jpg&h=b047603f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1URyWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1URyWM.jpg&h=1fa8b6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"